{"tid":412590,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"懷疑老母跌入騙局","createTime":"2017-09-24T19:12:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-26T04:43:54.000Z","uid":53780,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"74a7c7852519b4ad6d05ff50d7bce5a1e471950f","tid":412590,"uid":53780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T19:12:29.000Z","msg":"有冇精通投資既巴打可以幫下我<br />\n前幾日老母話佢班c9朋友介意佢玩<br />\n一隻叫&rdquo;mbi mfc club&quot; m幣咁既野<br />\n佢話半年番幾番咁，賺到笑<br />\n<br />\n咁我上網搵左d資料就話<br />\nm幣mbi公司發行既<br />\n限定6000萬個<br />\n個玩法係，例如你買左500hkd, 如果變左1000hkd<br />\n你想賣既話，只可以拎到（60%）600蚊，（10%）100會變左手續費，其餘既（30%）300蚊要投入去再買番m幣<br />\n<br />\n因為強制回購既原因，推升個幣值，再不停搵人加入，供不應求下，幣值就會只升不跌。<br />\n聽落m幣既幣值係建基於mbi呢間公司，如果佢突然收皮或者無人加入，姐係變左咩都無<br />\n<br />\n想問我理解有冇錯？<br />\n老母好似已經唔聲唔聲入左十皮<br />\n急問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9a85144df351d887045a92a65415a30a43aecf0","tid":412590,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T19:18:33.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"b88e191e7bc4354453c9723d449ed432c0ecf7b1","tid":412590,"uid":106544,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T19:23:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e48a9528fae9f93ab1fb23fd4700de7e8d5902ec","tid":412590,"uid":149852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T19:24:31.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"1003457a39b956885179370bc26c12b467a7ea01","tid":412590,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T19:34:17.000Z","msg":"因為強制回購既原因，推升個幣值，再不停搵人加入<br />\n<br />\n咪即係傳銷 屌"},{"pid":"25ae70c7145fb7221a2ecc092b9ec42bdaec6008","tid":412590,"uid":137647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T19:35:56.000Z","msg":"要翻成倍先賺果少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e216c85f5c19b983bb91c90aa55b202fb2a36c2","tid":412590,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201